Hidden Cobra 3
         Indicators - Watchlist
         DHS and FBI identified Internet Protocol (IP) addresses, and other indicators of compromise (IOCs), associated with a remote administration tool (RAT) which has been identified as JOANAP and BRAMBUL; used by the North Korean government. Note: The IOCs sighted date has a “Zulu” date-time stamp.
